:\"Style: Elegant, Minimalist, Sophisticated, Vintage-Inspired. Color palette: Black, Cream. Key pieces: Coat, Sheer Blouse, Pointed-Toe Heels, Fishnet Tights. Mood: Polished, Dramatic, Refined. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2004,2005,2006,2007],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/8c51c86b919b4f3feb569340f61dbf848b7b73178d44f7c35053e6d54a9b4022.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/8c51c86b919b4f3feb569340f61dbf848b7b73178d44f7c35053e6d54a9b4022.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"elegant\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Elegant, Minimalist, Sophisticated, Vintage-Inspired. Color palette: Black, Cream. Key pieces: Coat, Sheer Blouse, Pointed-Toe Heels, Fishnet Tights. Mood: Polished, Dramatic, Refined. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":464,\"public_id\":\"zAE8drrQTFJY\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.372818\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.372823\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Glamour Blazer Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated dark ensemble anchored by a black double-breasted blazer with statement red textured gloves and layered jewelry, creating a polished yet edgy aesthetic. The look balances formal tailoring with rebellious accessories for a modern gothic appeal.\",\"garment_ids\":[1952,1953,1957,1956],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/9c4ab07cbea940a073e97f609d65a3cf6a4f40329dfb33ae8fd3ce27fdea0b2a.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/9c4ab07cbea940a073e97f609d65a3cf6a4f40329dfb33ae8fd3ce27fdea0b2a.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Evening event, cocktail party, date night, avant-garde fashion setting\",\"season\":\"All-season\",\"formality\":\"semi-formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit masterfully balances structured tailoring with rebellious, edgy elements. The black blazer provides sophistication and polish, while the red lace gloves and layered chain necklaces inject drama and gothic glamour. The sheer lace harness bodysuit visible beneath adds an unexpected, provocative layer that elevates the look from basic formal wear to avant-garde and fashion-forward. The gold button details tie the palette together with a luxe finish. Best for someone confident in making a statement and embracing darker aesthetics.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":454,\"public_id\":\"9z9Qvt4Qgpg7\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T06:48:33.308338\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T06:48:52.744795\"},{\"name\":\"Casual Layered Mirror Selfie Look\",\"description\":\"A relaxed, effortlessly cool casual outfit featuring a charcoal ribbed knit sweater layered with a black V-neck undershirt, paired with light-wash denim and anchored with a burgundy leather belt. The look is completed with a black shoulder bag and delicate gold jewelry.\",\"garment_ids\":[1807,1808,1809,1810,1812],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/fc8fe3ee25df573b017ffdaebae144722e344bd882136c755bf3242ea5ac0801.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/fc8fe3ee25df573b017ffdaebae144722e344bd882136c755bf3242ea5ac0801.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Everyday casual wear, social media content creation, relaxed hangouts\",\"season\":\"Fall/Winter or all-season\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The outfit successfully balances layers with a relaxed fit, creating visual interest through color blocking and texture. The burgundy belt adds a touch of color without disrupting the cool-toned neutral palette. This is a classic TikTok/social media casual aesthetic that feels both put-together and effortlessly cool.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":408,\"public_id\":\"59AX8vIq3MZC\",\"user_