t, Black Tights, Platform Boots, Shoulder Bag. Mood: Sophisticated, Modern, Minimalist, Chic. Formality: smart casual (7/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[583,584,585,586,587],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/3e934df18f60eb0c81fec2048f88213568485bbef3b79e552d5f8e911ab6b413.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/3e934df18f60eb0c81fec2048f88213568485bbef3b79e552d5f8e911ab6b413.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Minimalist, Monochrome, Polished, Modern. Color palette: Gray, Black, Charcoal. Key pieces: Pinstripe Blazer, Pleated Skirt, Black Tights, Platform Boots, Shoulder Bag. Mood: Sophisticated, Modern, Minimalist, Chic. Formality: smart casual (7/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":111,\"public_id\":\"94ddbhI4mWBQ\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T20:07:57.586967\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T20:07:57.586972\"},{\"name\":\"School Uniform with Blazer\",\"description\":\"A classic school uniform ensemble featuring a structured blazer with emblem, white shirt, and navy striped tie, photographed in a car setting.\",\"garment_ids\":[469,470,471],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/6cadb6606e87fe6f0b5f71bffb27c4a2eaa019b4dc20aaa22d2abe06612d6bfb.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/6cadb6606e87fe6f0b5f71bffb27c4a2eaa019b4dc20aaa22d2abe06612d6bfb.webp\",\"occasion\":\"School, academic settings, official school events\",\"season\":\"all-season\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Classic European-style school uniform with traditional blazer, tie, and crisp white shirt. The emblem and structured tailoring indicate a formal educational institution. This uniform represents a timeless preppy aesthetic commonly found in international schools and traditional academic settings.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":85,\"public_id\":\"9ApU3T461XbC\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:24:29.119711\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:47.904524\"},{\"name\":\"Steampunk-Inspired Victorian Casual\",\"description\":\"A striking steampunk-themed outfit combining a crisp white button-up shirt with a burgundy leather corset-style vest, black tapered pants, and chunky red-and-black boots. The look is elevated with blue-mirrored sunglasses and coordinating accessories for an edgy, alternative aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[463,464,465,468,467],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/d594f3cd47bf0e29b40ae7fba77136aa55fab1d86bafa3cfc19d07988b9185b8.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/d594f3cd47bf0e29b40ae7fba77136aa55fab1d86bafa3cfc19d07988b9185b8.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Alternative fashion event, costume party, casual outing, music venue\",\"season\":\"Fall to early winter\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit successfully blends steampunk elements (corset vest, structured silhouette) with contemporary casual wear (modern sunglasses, tapered pants). The burgundy and black color scheme creates a cohesive, bold look, while the white shirt prevents the outfit from feeling too heavy. The lace-up boots reinforce the steampunk-industrial aesthetic. This is an excellent example of alternative fashion styling with clear personality and intentional design choices.\",\"is_owned\":true,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":84,\"public_id\":\"nujxAymgEBwx\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":1,\"last_worn\":\"2026-02-26T17:50:20.596702\",\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:23:13.822244\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:47.892453\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy All-Black Monochrome Look\",\"description\":\"A striking monochromatic black ensemble featuring a leather trench coat over a mini dress with knee-high boots, creating a sleek and edgy aesthetic perfect for making a bold statement.\",\"garment_ids\":[434,435,436,437,438,439],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/3998bb686c9a9112c533f60e6be986a87e7dc936f9c7e9876134043f2fae5f2d.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/3998bb686c9a9112c533f60e6be986a87e7dc936f9c7e9876134043f2fae5f2d.webp\",\"occasion\":\"City strolling, casual meetings, or evening social events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The monochromatic black palette creates a powerful, confident look while the single gold accent adds sophistication. Perfect proportions with the flowing coat over fitted dress and boots.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":81,\"public_id\":\"E3jkbccGAd6S\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.764558\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:46.378091\"},{\"name\":\"Professional Polka Dot Suit Set\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated charcoal grey suit with white polka dot pattern paired with a crisp white shirt, creating a polished business-casual look with a playful twist.\",\"garment_ids\":[426,427,428,433,430,432],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/fd06d470a229587be0b17b29bed179d0ef0821d01fd59cd79a779539666561a0.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/fd06d470a229587be0b17b29bed179d0ef0821d01fd59cd79a779539666561a0.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Business meetings, office work, professional presentations\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The polka dot pattern adds visual interest to an otherwise traditional suit, making it perfect for professional settings where personality can shine through\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":80,\"public_id\":\"fofpOTnLdQ3J\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.760066\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:43.881032\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Victorian Inspired Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic dark ensemble featuring ornate brocade fabrics with luxurious fur trim, creating an opulent gothic aesthetic with Victorian influences.\",\"garment_ids\":[423,424,425],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c7b025de186bfd325c93b200bec5efa00980139368a255632dacabb6fbf5c227.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/c7b025de186bfd325c93b200bec5efa00980139368a255632dacabb6fbf5c227.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Formal evening event or theatrical performance\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit combines gothic aesthetics with Victorian opulence through rich textures, ornate patterns, and dramatic fur accents, perfect for formal evening occasions\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":79,\"public_id\":\"idy7ELRfCisE\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.755270\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:43.412165\"},{\"name\":\"Monochrome Professional Chic\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated black and white ensemble featuring a fitted white blazer over a black bra top paired with a form-fitting black mini skirt and black stockings.\",\"garment_ids\":[418,419,420,421,422],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/cb88d12ba387a7460004c938b2969b9259045707c256c4918a30df5e3e3e9dab.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/cb88d12ba387a7460004c938b2969b9259045707c256c4918a30df5e3e3e9dab.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Creative workplace, evening networking event, or modern business meeting\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The open blazer over visible undergarment creates a modern twist on professional wear, while the monochromatic palette keeps it sophisticated\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":78,\"public_id\":\"LHzhiekrt2FY\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.751448\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:43.280104\"},{\"name\":\"Off-Shoulder Bow Top with Plaid Mini Skirt\",\"description\":\"A feminine and playful outfit featuring an off-shoulder black top with white bow detail paired with a plaid mini skirt and thigh-high boots, creating a cute schoolgirl-inspired aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[413,414,415,416,417],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/72914d85bbf8b717e8cfef107c042c9710699ed80cdce306f7fdcb8f196273c2.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/72914d85bbf8b717e8cfef107c042c9710699ed80cdce306f7fdcb8f196273c2.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, dates, or social events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The outfit successfully balances sweet and edgy elements with the bow detail contrasting the thigh-high boots, while the plaid skirt adds a preppy touch\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":77,\"public_id\":\"loT1paQb2GHB\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.747404\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:42.780644\"},{\"name\":\"Chic Business Casual Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated monochromatic look featuring a sleek black fitted top paired with a flowing tan midi skirt, creating an elegant silhouette perfect for professional or semi-formal occasions.\",\"garment_ids\":[409,410,411,412],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/859f2bd555170a413f325d9bead77bba1b881b0871a06ffef746a75c0a53b375.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/859f2bd555170a413f325d9bead77bba1b881b0871a06ffef746a75c0a53b375.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Office work, business meetings, or professional events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the fitted black top and flowing tan skirt creates visual interest while maintaining professional appropriateness. The monochromatic accessories tie the look together seamlessly.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":76,\"public_id\":\"liYbE0P2xoJE\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.743440\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:42.004505\"},{\"name\":\"Cozy Sage Sweater and Maxi Skirt Look\",\"description\":\"A comfortable yet elegant autumn outfit featuring a chunky sage green turtleneck sweater paired with a flowing black maxi skirt and sleek black boots.\",\"garment_ids\":[404,405,406,407,408],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/6d3ad675b41ffeeebcc2251a3a5d31c9cff98de2a90ea8b1e6a94ef77479a4be.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/6d3ad675b41ffeeebcc2251a3a5d31c9cff98de2a90ea8b1e6a94ef77479a4be.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee dates, weekend errands\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Perfect balance of comfort and style with the cozy sweater contrasting beautifully against the sleek black pieces. The platform boots add an edgy touch to an otherwise soft and feminine silhouette.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":75,\"public_id\":\"duRKJ7JGOzeK\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.739201\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:40.994927\"},{\"name\":\"Long Herringbone Coat with Black Mini Dress\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated ensemble featuring a floor-length herringbone wool coat worn over a sleek black mini dress, completed with tall black boots and sheer tights for an elegant yet edgy autumn look.\",\"garment_ids\":[399,400,401,402,403],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/705db7db19aa201b238f94332922dba7df27f922bbd035fe04fdceb06d888fae.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/705db7db19aa201b238f94332922dba7df27f922bbd035fe04fdceb06d888fae.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Urban professional or sophisticated daytime event\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The dramatic length of the herringbone coat creates striking proportions while the all-black base keeps the look grounded and sophisticated\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":74,\"public_id\":\"TId6WLxO9wTY\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.732804\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:40.706983\"},{\"name\":\"Urban Oversized Leather Bomber Look\",\"description\":\"A contemporary street-style ensemble featuring an oversized black leather bomber jacket paired with black mini bottoms and statement fuzzy boots, creating a bold urban aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[394,395,396,397,398],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/70e7fd34552abe44ddcef6946e724c0ebb6f6e9c8d55431204746f5f03b3503f.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/70e7fd34552abe44ddcef6946e724c0ebb6f6e9c8d55431204746f5f03b3503f.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual city outings, nightlife, or fashion-forward street wear\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized leather jacket creates dramatic proportions balanced by fitted bottoms, while the fuzzy boots add textural interest and height\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":73,\"public_id\":\"0Elasm8LCsOS\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.728410\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:40.377846\