 an oversized beige hoodie with dramatic faux fur hood, black studded shorts, sheer tights, and chunky platform boots for an edgy urban aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[349,350,351,352,353],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/da3e4d8e1ae01b23556db8c00a62594f98ac363c7a1b0fefcf999dd20384116b.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/da3e4d8e1ae01b23556db8c00a62594f98ac363c7a1b0fefcf999dd20384116b.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, concerts, creative events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized fur hood creates a striking focal point while the platform boots add height and attitude. The contrast between soft textures and hard hardware creates visual interest.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":65,\"public_id\":\"GWcsDETqfM4L\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.684935\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:30.892536\"},{\"name\":\"Minimalist Black and Cream Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated monochromatic outfit featuring a cream oversized sweater paired with a flowing black maxi skirt, creating an elegant contrast with minimalist styling.\",\"garment_ids\":[345,346,347,348],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/ec8f6910eb18ca3f4ab5cc23e214a86cdafb510556666e480a2cbafca68b8f20.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/ec8f6910eb18ca3f4ab5cc23e214a86cdafb510556666e480a2cbafca68b8f20.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee date, or relaxed weekend activities\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the oversized cream sweater and flowing black skirt creates visual interest while maintaining a cohesive, understated aesthetic. The long braid adds a feminine touch to the clean lines.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":64,\"public_id\":\"g32rf8kvtG6o\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:11:10.676504\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:30.215525\"},{\"name\":\"Glamorous White Fur and Black Mini Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A striking evening look featuring a luxurious white faux fur cropped jacket paired with a sleek black bodycon mini skirt, creating a bold contrast of textures and colors.\",\"garment_ids\":[340,341,342,343,344],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/534a5b74037e39bbb37a76191abf5850c033f6ccb9677f50cd5701fca51b18a3.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/534a5b74037e39bbb37a76191abf5850c033f6ccb9677f50cd5701fca51b18a3.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Upscale evening events, parties, or nightlife\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"semi-formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"bold\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the fluffy white fur and sleek black pieces creates visual interest and sophistication. The cropped proportions and bodycon silhouette add a modern, youthful edge to the luxurious materials.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":63,\"public_id\":\"5YeCNECyFrwn\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:08:39.355720\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:29.294374\"},{\"name\":\"Layered Off-Shoulder Casual Look\",\"description\":\"A trendy layered outfit featuring an off-shoulder black top over a white collared shirt, paired with gray flare jeans and accessorized with a burgundy shoulder bag.\",\"garment_ids\":[335,336,337,338,339],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/1f660186a941c305a844b754d3ca12adc7924a4b1f079cdc573ee7010c88667c.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/1f660186a941c305a844b754d3ca12adc7924a4b1f079cdc573ee7010c88667c.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee date, shopping\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The layering technique creates visual interest while the flare jeans add a retro touch. The burgundy accessories tie the look together cohesively.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":62,\"public_id\":\"JE5VoJAYsQBj\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:08:06.934146\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:29.137414\"},{\"name\":\"All-Black Winter Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A monochromatic black outfit featuring a wool coat over a pleated skirt with tights, creating a classic and sophisticated winter look.\",\"garment_ids\":[330,331,332,333],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/1735746b52d6f30e9b651d42776ab3af34befab497b5ca033e35729405f4d893.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/1735746b52d6f30e9b651d42776ab3af34befab497b5ca033e35729405f4d893.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Work, casual meetings, or city errands\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The all-black monochromatic palette creates a sleek, timeless look with the pleated skirt adding feminine detail to balance the structured coat.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":61,\"public_id\":\"5e9jyzqxoVpq\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T17:07:38.126368\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:28.073914\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Fantasy Cosplay Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic fantasy-inspired costume featuring a navy blue strappy lingerie set paired with white opera gloves and a dark cape, creating a gothic medieval aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[326,327,328,329],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/d6c3c0e9c112da89455f59414ae09c2bea40886a93d6bdf57a26025724cadc6a.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/d6c3c0e9c112da89455f59414ae09c2bea40886a93d6bdf57a26025724cadc6a.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Costume party, cosplay event, or themed photoshoot\",\"season\":\"All-season indoor event\",\"formality\":\"costume\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"revealing\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the revealing navy lingerie set and the formal white gloves creates a striking fantasy aesthetic, while the dark cape adds dramatic flair typical of gothic or medieval-inspired costumes.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":60,\"public_id\":\"T6opaOAItXnj\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:29:56.292965\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:27.744242\"},{\"name\":\"Academic Fantasy Layered Looks\",\"description\":\"Four distinct fantasy-inspired outfits featuring layered knitwear, pleated skirts, and medieval-style accessories creating a dark academia aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[320,319,318,321,322,323,325],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/9d16ffa75a3929031d4fc6f3f2dda85f35a5ff9f100e514a3e601a2e5301540b.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/9d16ffa75a3929031d4fc6f3f2dda85f35a5ff9f100e514a3e601a2e5301540b.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, creative events, costume parties\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"vintage\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"These outfits blend academic preppy style with fantasy elements through leather accessories and layered textures. The consistent use of pleated skirts and knit layers creates cohesion while leather harnesses and decorative belts add gothic fantasy touches.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":59,\"public_id\":\"Y2NWQhekJpwx\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:06:04.366323\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:26.333982\"},{\"name\":\"Dark Academia Plaid Skirt Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated dark academia-inspired outfit featuring a fitted charcoal turtleneck paired with a pleated plaid mini skirt, black tights, and knee-high boots for a polished collegiate look.\",\"garment_ids\":[307,308,309,310,311],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/bcee211e7b366c53a67e4e5b3339a4e7f48efd72d82c7eeaeca194109119c567.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/bcee211e7b366c53a67e4e5b3339a4e7f48efd72d82c7eeaeca194109119c567.webp\",\"occasion\":\"School, casual meetings, coffee dates\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Perfect dark academia aesthetic with the classic plaid and turtleneck combination. The monochromatic color scheme keeps it sophisticated while the mini skirt adds youthful appeal.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":58,\"public_id\":\"fdaTRSyJ6wLD\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:05:25.232066\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:25.988729\"},{\"name\":\"Dark Academia Layered Look\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated dark academia ensemble featuring layered neutral tones with a brown leather harness vest over a cream shirt, paired with a pleated mini skirt and knee-high socks.\",\"garment_ids\":[301,302,303,306,305],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/0f6d5c66b702ca79ef2a510758d1a29182c6073eb953a313383b68c25f2346ac.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/0f6d5c66b702ca79ef2a510758d1a29182c6073eb953a313383b68c25f2346ac.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual school/university or creative workplace\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"vintage\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Perfect blend of preppy school uniform elements with edgy leather harness details, creating a sophisticated dark academia aesthetic\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":57,\"public_id\":\"PImCGOV7XPTB\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:04:59.662087\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:25.568890\"},{\"name\":\"Layered Bohemian Casual Look\",\"description\":\"A relaxed bohemian-inspired outfit featuring layered pieces with a long duster cardigan over a black camisole and high-waisted jeans, finished with lace-up boots.\",\"garment_ids\":[294,295,296,297,298,299],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/e620c398156c44d9efad35afc3f13e52e1919bd2146f53773b172ce07812232e.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/e620c398156c44d9efad35afc3f13e52e1919bd2146f53773b172ce07812232e.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee dates, weekend activities\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"bohemian\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The flowing cardigan creates beautiful movement while the fitted base layers maintain a flattering silhouette. The earthy color palette is cohesive and versatile.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":56,\"public_id\":\"x3PlvjWs5p4O\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:04:28.162867\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:25.208676\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy All-Black Leather Look\",\"description\":\"A bold monochromatic outfit featuring an oversized black leather jacket layered over a fitted black mini dress, completed with knee-high black boots for an edgy, rock-inspired aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[290,291,292,293],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/770e492f2962b2225e8eaa2e55cf4db986b5cd6fc38489ae7f5a70580de03877.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/770e492f2962b2225e8eaa2e55cf4db986b5cd6fc38489ae7f5a70580de03877.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Night out, concerts, casual social events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Perfect example of mixing proportions with oversized outerwear and fitted underlayers; the monochromatic palette creates sophistication while leather adds edge\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":55,\"public_id\":\"5QL5m9W9TasM\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:03:56.362611\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:25.012326\"},{\"name\":\"Monochromatic Taupe Street Style\",\"description\":\"A cohesive monochromatic look featuring layered taupe tones with leather textures and platform sneakers for an effortless urban aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[285,286,287,288,289],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/1406ded73b2ab0a8712cb508225a5532cf2f42cb11204229c083f397ed4af19c.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/1406ded73b2ab0a8712cb508225a5532cf2f42cb11204229c083f397ed4af19c.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, street style photography, urban exploring\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"streetwear\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Perfect example of tonal dressing with mixed textures - the leather jacket elevates the casual hoodie and joggers combination\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":54,\"public_id\":\"uGHrmz7APCEr\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:03:31.765689\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:24.889788\"},{\"name\":\"Minimalist Monochrome Look\",\"description\":\"A clean, modern outfit featuring a crisp white turtleneck paired with a black midi skirt and combat boots for an effortlessly chic aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[281,282,283,284],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c91aacd71a82fe3767ed475a55e2d349267b75b063197e32278c92daa25fdcdd.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/c91aacd71a82fe3767ed475a55e2d349267b75b063197e32278c92daa25fdcdd.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee dates, or relaxed work environment\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the soft turtleneck and edgy boots creates perfect balance, while the side slit adds subtle allure to an otherwise conservative look\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":53,\"public_id\":\"yfvhtp9t3wFs\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:03:03.263722\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:24.578785\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Urban Street Style\",\"description\":\"A contemporary streetwear look combining an oversized black leather bomber jacket with cargo shorts and layered statement jewelry for an effortlessly cool aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[277,278,279,280],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/59f6b975283b24d62715f713d8d5b037391275d0a5323ff7c59a580ca07428d3.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/59f6b975283b24d62715f713d8d5b037391275d0a5323ff7c59a580ca07428d3.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, shopping, urban exploration\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized leather jacket creates interesting proportions when paired with fitted bottoms, while layered jewelry adds personality to the monochromatic base\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":52,\"public_id\":\"ULNSbPsDdudU\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:02:35.965120\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:24.250610\"},{\"name\":\"Burgundy Pinstripe Power Look\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated business-casual ensemble featuring a burgundy pinstripe blazer with black accents, dark flared jeans, and coordinating burgundy accessories for a polished yet modern professional look.\",\"garment_ids\":[264,265,266,270,268,269,276],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/89aa195ca4e7b37aadc46732b57ed7b746cfd0f2199e21aece8cf721320a95ce.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/89aa195ca4e7b37aadc46732b57ed7b746cfd0f2199e21aece8cf721320a95ce.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Business casual office or professional meeting\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The menswear-inspired tie and structured blazer create authority while the flared jeans and platform shoes add contemporary flair. The coordinated burgundy accessories show attention to detail.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":51,\"public_id\":\"8zIH4kl1KHRI\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:02:09.908133\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:23.907383\"},{\"name\":\"Dramatic Black Power Coat Look\",\"description\":\"A striking all-black ensemble featuring an oversized double-breasted coat worn over what appears to be a fitted dress or top, creating a powerful and sophisticated silhouette with dramatic proportions.\",\"garment_ids\":[260,261,262,263],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/165f18d598a0c80930fd72b2bc394574fca9d1709c602ab2e30750fe4cfea100.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/165f18d598a0c80930fd72b2bc394574fca9d1709c602ab2e30750fe4cfea100.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Business meetings, formal events, fashion-forward occasions\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized coat creates a powerful silhouette while the monochromatic black palette adds sophistication and elegance. The contrast between the structured outerwear and fitted underlayer creates visual interest through proportions rather than color.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":50,\"public_id\":\"DQkReKycZydN\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:01:30.156139\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:22.755093\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Academia Long Coat Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic all-black outfit featuring layered gothic-inspired pieces with academic undertones, perfect for making a bold statement in cooler weather.\",\"garment_ids\":[254,255,256,257,258,259],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/13ec4e8cb4b25c02f983d06eb09726b68dc92aa1c7fab608ef06361c2340aafa.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/13ec4e8cb4b25c02f983d06eb09726b68dc92aa1c7fab608ef06361c2340aafa.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Creative events, fashion shows, or statement-making outings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The dramatic length contrast between the long coat and mini skirt creates visual interest, while the white accessories provide striking contrast points\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":49,\"public_id\":\"dUlnnXvBVI2W\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:01:01.418983\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:22.745801\"},{\"name\":\"Contemporary Business Professional\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated layered ensemble combining a structured black blazer with contrasting white lapels, paired with a metallic leather skirt and statement accessories for a modern professional look.\",\"garment_ids\":[247,248,249,251,252],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/38b85fadb22e966e1050384ec78311b38ec84e67eae140c83b6396b17edfaf03.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/38b85fadb22e966e1050384ec78311b38ec84e67eae140c83b6396b17edfaf03.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Business meetings, corporate events, modern workplace\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The color-blocked blazer creates visual interest while the metallic skirt and strappy boots add contemporary edge to traditional suiting. The cat-eye glasses provide intellectual sophistication.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":48,\"public_id\":\"2mvv253tMc4T\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T09:00:27.073960\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:21.434448\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Lolita Cosplay Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic gothic lolita inspired costume featuring a long white coat with black trim, layered over dark clothing, accessorized with ornate hair decorations and boots.\",\"garment_ids\":[242,243,244,246],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/37bb5769b52c07662760ab78f646ae3023219b4aa67e18bbb58079bd63c0bff9.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/37bb5769b52c07662760ab78f646ae3023219b4aa67e18bbb58079bd63c0bff9.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Costume party or cosplay event\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Dramatic costume look perfect for gothic lolita or anime cosplay, featuring contrasting white and black elements with ornate accessories\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":47,\"public_id\":\"BdEw3ooGve0c\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:07:32.306752\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:20.550206\"},{\"name\":\"Victorian Lolita Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A romantic Victorian-inspired Lolita coordinate featuring a cream ruffled blouse with navy trim and a voluminous navy blue high-waisted skirt with suspender details.\",\"garment_ids\":[238,239,240,241],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/d806d3ba030d09e65e2223e5cb57e8acdc22b67086e9d094f0827b55cce4ab98.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/d806d3ba030d09e65e2223e5cb57e8acdc22b67086e9d094f0827b55cce4ab98.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Cosplay events, themed parties, or alternative fashion gatherings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Classic Lolita coordinate with excellent attention to Victorian details and proper proportions between the fitted bodice and voluminous skirt\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":46,\"public_id\":\"dFOP77fnrcrd\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:07:05.173251\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:14.182025\"},{\"name\":\"Monochrome Corset Suit\",\"description\":\"A striking black and white ensemble featuring a structured white corset top paired with a coordinating black oversized blazer and wide-leg trousers for a modern power dressing look.\",\"garment_ids\":[233,234,235,236,237],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/18e85f2b47a8860c92a34d70bf6d3b58f62e63032e506dd4111c1754a6f686a2.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/18e85f2b47a8860c92a34d70bf6d3b58f62e63032e506dd4111c1754a6f686a2.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Fashion-forward business meeting or sophisticated dinner\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"semi-formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the structured corset and oversized blazer creates visual interest while maintaining sophistication. The wide-leg trousers balance the fitted top beautifully.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":45,\"public_id\":\"xa3C30YpQxhO\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:06:38.646186\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:20.124377\"},{\"name\":\"Burgundy Pinstripe Business Chic\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated business-casual ensemble featuring a burgundy pinstripe shirt paired with a black leather mini skirt and luxury accessories. The look is elevated with red crystal nail art and classic black patent pumps.\",\"garment_ids\":[224,225,232,227,228,229],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/ae8f90f6f1dc02918ddbc59869c710d372c833b96ae14c38f1597d091e33e47a.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/ae8f90f6f1dc02918ddbc59869c710d372c833b96ae14c38f1597d091e33e47a.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Office, business lunch, or upscale social event\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Cohesive burgundy and black color scheme with luxury designer touches creates a sophisticated yet approachable professional look\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":44,\"public_id\":\"ySUphHIKDcxH\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:06:10.280838\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:13.717901\"},{\"name\":\"Off-Shoulder Knit and Black Dress Combo\",\"description\":\"A creative layered look featuring a black fit-and-flare mini dress worn underneath a gray ribbed knit off-shoulder sweater, creating an interesting contrast of textures and styles.\",\"garment_ids\":[221,222,223],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/bbbe60b81216738a607f85f0b5dcc088733297f74f4d06d6c14558f1c06efa80.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/bbbe60b81216738a607f85f0b5dcc088733297f74f4d06d6c14558f1c06efa80.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outing or weekend brunch\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The off-shoulder styling of the sweater creates an unexpected and fashionable layering technique, balancing the sweetness of the mini dress with cozy knitwear\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":43,\"public_id\":\"64929UaPKZfh\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:05:32.340835\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:20.044695\"},{\"name\":\"School Uniform with Cardigan\",\"description\":\"A classic Japanese school uniform featuring a fitted cardigan over a collared shirt with a pleated skirt, creating a traditional academic look.\",\"garment_ids\":[218,219,220],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/f987981cf93737fd90a625cd615a992869495a956f681807452a8becd1748ad3.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/f987981cf93737fd90a625cd615a992869495a956f681807452a8becd1748ad3.webp\",\"occasion\":\"School or academic setting\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Traditional Japanese school uniform styling with layered knitwear for warmth and formality\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":42,\"public_id\":\"fovVmcFkFMzB\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:05:08.102882\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:56.674072\"},{\"name\":\"Romantic Ruffled Denim Midi Set\",\"description\":\"A feminine and contemporary outfit featuring a dramatic white cold-shoulder ruffle blouse paired with a tiered denim midi skirt and nude pointed-toe heels.\",\"garment_ids\":[214,215,216],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/b7ae6a1af02615b24acb6d371fc63c940dae8b31b15eb009dc87060e0f3ba34c.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/b7ae6a1af02615b24acb6d371fc63c940dae8b31b15eb009dc87060e0f3ba34c.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Brunch date or casual office event\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between feminine ruffles and structured denim creates an interesting juxtaposition; nude heels ground the look without competing with the statement pieces\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":41,\"public_id\":\"DRsZ28690sT4\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:04:41.114290\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:19.489119\"},{\"name\":\"Monochromatic Gothic Platform Look\",\"description\":\"An all-black ensemble featuring a long leather coat with fur trim, mini dress, thigh-high stockings, and chunky platform boots. The look is completed with a studded handbag for an edgy gothic aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[209,210,211,212,213],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/2e995f9ba74a5cdfeb419062252089304596f4194519009266c009e5cea05ea3.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/2e995f9ba74a5cdfeb419062252089304596f4194519009266c009e5cea05ea3.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Night out, concert, or fashion-forward casual event\",\"season\":\"fall/winter\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the luxurious fur-trimmed coat and edgy platform boots creates an interesting high-low mix, while the thigh-high stockings add a provocative element to the monochromatic palette.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":40,\"public_id\":\"j6rB43orALvF\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:04:15.593458\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:18.739236\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Leather Matrix Look\",\"description\":\"A bold all-black ensemble featuring a dramatic floor-length leather trench coat over a white button-up shirt, mini skirt, and knee-high boots for a sleek, edgy aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[203,204,205,206,207,208],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/58e7eb44e6a7fddd468bcba548ac3811b1b87a7279448a1ff728ec2241b747fa.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/58e7eb44e6a7fddd468bcba548ac3811b1b87a7279448a1ff728ec2241b747fa.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Evening out, fashion events, or artistic gatherings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The dramatic leather trench creates a powerful silhouette while the white shirt provides contrast. The choker adds gothic flair to this sophisticated yet rebellious look.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":39,\"public_id\":\"8iXxu6SLOfj7\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:03:46.695171\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:12.974552\"},{\"name\":\"Cozy Blue Cable Knit School Girl Look\",\"description\":\"A cute and cozy outfit featuring an oversized blue cable knit sweater paired with a pleated mini skirt, knee-high socks, and platform Mary Jane shoes for a sweet academic aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[198,199,200,201,202],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/175b806f85bfadce2b1650e822143f41cef1645922573ede253fe9116982a089.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/175b806f85bfadce2b1650e822143f41cef1645922573ede253fe9116982a089.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual daily wear, school, weekend outings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized cable knit hoodie creates a cozy contrast with the structured pleated skirt, while the knee-high socks and platform Mary Janes complete the sweet academic aesthetic. The monochromatic blue palette is grounded by black accessories.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":38,\"public_id\":\"TiHVzWZxr1Ob\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:03:17.778636\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:17.456419\"},{\"name\":\"Layered Grunge Academia\",\"description\":\"A grunge-inspired academic look featuring layered textures with a light blue corset top, oversized sage green jacket with fur trim, and a pleated neutral skirt.\",\"garment_ids\":[193,194,195,196,197],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/6df96345d6bd2a261160a83d169c659285d4d273ebd897fca94393fb7a5dc9ea.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/6df96345d6bd2a261160a83d169c659285d4d273ebd897fca94393fb7a5dc9ea.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, creative environments, or artistic events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The combination of structured corset styling with oversized outerwear and fur trim creates an interesting contrast between fitted and relaxed silhouettes, perfect for the grunge revival trend.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":37,\"public_id\":\"kD7DbgoNftR2\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:02:47.401448\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:12.106788\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Brown Leather Moto Look\",\"description\":\"A bold rock-inspired outfit featuring a rich brown leather moto jacket paired with black studded pants and dramatic accessories for an edgy, rebellious aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[189,190,192],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/af277efa9c168461d5dd42d43d1c1994fc2efd80749dfa8d6d3c06e7196c63e1.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/af277efa9c168461d5dd42d43d1c1994fc2efd80749dfa8d6d3c06e7196c63e1.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, concerts, or night out\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the tough leather moto jacket and sweet hair bow creates an interesting juxtaposition of edgy and feminine elements\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":36,\"public_id\":\"gEo2AUFbEmJi\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:02:19.984535\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:17.125335\"},{\"name\":\"Preppy Pinstripe School Look\",\"description\":\"A classic preppy ensemble featuring an oversized pinstripe blazer layered over a white collared shirt, paired with a black pleated skirt and knee-high boots for a sophisticated school-girl aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[182,183,184,188,186,187],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c3e565bf7cb1cba761b5b5c8eb9002c19ddaeaed2f28a19325b5ad2cdf290ac8.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/c3e565bf7cb1cba761b5b5c8eb9002c19ddaeaed2f28a19325b5ad2cdf290ac8.webp\",\"occasion\":\"School, casual business, or smart-casual social events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The oversized blazer creates a modern take on classic preppy style, while the pleated skirt and knee-high boots maintain feminine elements\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":35,\"public_id\":\"hB9ZduaBLGYX\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:01:49.151186\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:56.236503\"},{\"name\":\"Olive Utility Midi Dress with Brown Accents\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated vintage-inspired look featuring an olive green midi dress layered with a brown sheer blouse and finished with matching brown accessories for a cohesive autumn ensemble.\",\"garment_ids\":[178,179,180,181],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/65b73e1febc0b1f13818cb1f76c1ec5f66ec3e615de425b62b7d9b49e74488fa.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/65b73e1febc0b1f13818cb1f76c1ec5f66ec3e615de425b62b7d9b49e74488fa.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee date, or weekend brunch\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"vintage\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The layering of the sheer brown blouse under the olive dress creates visual interest while the matching brown boots tie the look together beautifully. The black belt provides contrast and waist definition.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":34,\"public_id\":\"CVJgRQO5ji53\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:01:19.087654\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:11.390394\"},{\"name\":\"Cozy White Sweater Dress Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A comfortable and stylish outfit featuring an oversized white cable-knit sweater dress layered with dark tights and topped with chunky knit leg warmers for a cozy, winter-ready look.\",\"garment_ids\":[173,174,175,176,177],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/982140707844835d64db196559eb997fcb689c7df677c2343607ef0c3132165f.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/982140707844835d64db196559eb997fcb689c7df677c2343607ef0c3132165f.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Weekend outings, casual coffee dates, or relaxed social gatherings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The outfit successfully combines comfort with style through thoughtful layering and texture mixing. The chunky leg warmers add visual interest while maintaining the cozy aesthetic.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":33,\"public_id\":\"lIcEir7fN0O2\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T08:00:41.356051\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:16.359298\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Lolita Inspired Dark Romance\",\"description\":\"A dramatic gothic-inspired ensemble featuring a black studded corset dress with chain details, paired with fishnet stockings and platform boots for an edgy romantic aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[167,168,172,170,171],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/05fd2efd7f29fa5d6385a135dffdf3533c46c2fcb6f97b063816aa4a0a3ddf69.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/05fd2efd7f29fa5d6385a135dffdf3533c46c2fcb6f97b063816aa4a0a3ddf69.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Alternative fashion events, concerts, creative gatherings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Strong gothic aesthetic with romantic corset elements balanced by edgy punk accessories like fishnets and platform boots\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":32,\"public_id\":\"73DxHcwEB9jJ\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:59:54.303951\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:10.893836\"},{\"name\":\"Classic Black and White Professional\",\"description\":\"A timeless monochromatic outfit featuring a crisp white button-up shirt tucked into a high-waisted black pencil skirt, completed with sheer black hosiery and black pumps for a polished, professional look.\",\"garment_ids\":[162,163,164,165,166],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c7c41929a49c1f9907442a7925ff0ab31e5b5cb1068566754276bfaf01c9f6a7.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/c7c41929a49c1f9907442a7925ff0ab31e5b5cb1068566754276bfaf01c9f6a7.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Office work, business meetings, professional events\",\"season\":\"Fall/Winter\",\"formality\":\"business-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"classic\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"A perfectly executed monochromatic professional look that emphasizes clean lines and classic tailoring. The high-waisted skirt creates an elegant silhouette, while the hosiery adds a polished finishing touch.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":31,\"public_id\":\"k42x1UsOkyQA\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:59:23.953485\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:15.972339\"},{\"name\":\"Luxe Faux Fur Winter Chic\",\"description\":\"A glamorous winter outfit featuring a dramatic white faux fur jacket layered over a black mini dress, elevated with statement jewelry and knee-high platform boots for an edgy-luxe aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[156,157,158,159,160,161],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/27922f499490576d4efdc32d081a5bd31497e60ced0a036dc40661285ecc3208.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/27922f499490576d4efdc32d081a5bd31497e60ced0a036dc40661285ecc3208.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual social outings, shopping, trendy events\",\"season\":\"winter\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the luxurious faux fur and edgy platform boots creates a high-low mix that's very current in fashion. The layered jewelry and visible socks add trendy styling details.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":30,\"public_id\":\"7LtyHXmyU6Hf\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:58:57.594850\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:56.117472\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Dark Romance Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic gothic-inspired look featuring an off-shoulder black top, leather corset belt, and layered accessories creating a dark romantic aesthetic with medieval undertones.\",\"garment_ids\":[150,151,155,153,154],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/4ae22b18bc4972286f24ea574511130e1db55249849ec44fb785ea07a49b23b3.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/4ae22b18bc4972286f24ea574511130e1db55249849ec44fb785ea07a49b23b3.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Alternative fashion events or themed parties\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"revealing\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Strong gothic aesthetic with leather accessories and romantic Victorian elements creating a dramatic dark fantasy look\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":29,\"public_id\":\"YJFLGYhP4ktO\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:58:27.177440\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:15.193487\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Romance Off-Shoulder Look\",\"description\":\"A dramatic romantic gothic ensemble featuring an off-shoulder white blouse paired with a black lace-up corset and flowing skirt, completed with thigh-high stockings for an edgy feminine aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[146,147,148,149],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/d60f80245b5afaf8c010a2ec461d89d90ce15447b49aaa87a8b62e5d416886b8.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/d60f80245b5afaf8c010a2ec461d89d90ce15447b49aaa87a8b62e5d416886b8.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Party, date night, or creative social events\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the innocent white blouse and structured black corset creates a compelling duality. The thigh-high stockings add vintage burlesque influence while maintaining sophistication.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":28,\"public_id\":\"aSgOKCdGHV13\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:57:58.261103\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:14.633722\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Autumn Midi Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated fall look combining a fitted black long-sleeve top with a brown plaid midi skirt, anchored by a studded leather belt and elevated with sleek ankle boots and a slouchy leather bag.\",\"garment_ids\":[140,141,142,143,144],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/b6302ae81b6686cee2718100af9905f30ec8a404de69bc696ccaf2cb896fa4b0.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/b6302ae81b6686cee2718100af9905f30ec8a404de69bc696ccaf2cb896fa4b0.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual weekend outings or creative workplace\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the flowing plaid skirt and fitted black top creates visual balance, while the studded belt adds personality and structure to the silhouette\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":27,\"public_id\":\"X5HstMJjARet\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:57:32.763843\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:55.144576\"},{\"name\":\"Sophisticated Winter Layering Look\",\"description\":\"An elegant monochromatic ensemble featuring a long dark coat over a cream turtleneck and leather mini skirt, completed with sleek boots and leather gloves for a refined winter aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[134,135,136,137,138,139],\"image_url\":\"/up