6cda576ce7d3530601d8dd6.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, conventions, creative events\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Anime-inspired kawaii fashion combining edgy streetwear with romantic gothic lolita elements, perfect for fans of Japanese fashion subcultures\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":17,\"public_id\":\"uhZUPJGmVZre\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:53:07.433891\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:03.987808\"},{\"name\":\"Cozy Off-Shoulder Sweater Look\",\"description\":\"A relaxed casual outfit featuring a cream off-shoulder knit sweater layered over a tank top, paired with dark tights and brown boots for a comfortable autumn aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[83,84,85,88,87],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/708764301374e4fba907b91eea42cc36fab1d053eb9c3d8d90f662046ebf8400.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/708764301374e4fba907b91eea42cc36fab1d053eb9c3d8d90f662046ebf8400.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Weekend brunch, coffee dates, casual outings\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"bohemian\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The off-shoulder sweater creates an effortlessly chic look while the tights and boots combination provides warmth and style for cooler weather\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":16,\"public_id\":\"5L9XoHzeygPr\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:52:29.168661\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:37:07.865942\"},{\"name\":\"Grunge Academia Plaid Set\",\"description\":\"A coordinated grunge-inspired look featuring a brown plaid pleated mini skirt paired with a matching plaid vest layered over an oversized olive military-style jacket and cream turtleneck.\",\"garment_ids\":[76,77,78,79,80,81],