          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 124097,
            "text": "[{\"name\":\"Deconstructed Grunge Plaid Look\",\"description\":\"A edgy, streetwear-inspired outfit featuring a plaid off-shoulder top paired with distressed, deconstructed cargo jeans.\",\"garment_ids\":[2317,2318,2319],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/83dc19af86d4c458ec8647d30ee5c07cd432c927dacb95f2f83e2df09c1c6822.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/83dc19af86d4c458ec8647d30ee5c07cd432c927dacb95f2f83e2df09c1c6822.webp\",\"occasion\":\"casual\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The outfit balances a feminine off-shoulder silhouette with raw, deconstructed denim for a high-contrast streetwear aesthetic.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":518,\"public_id\":\"rQWJOVP3etKX\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-08T00:11:47.451294\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-08T00:11:47.451298\"},{\"name\":\"Goth-Grunge Layered Aesthetic\",\"description\":\"A dark, edgy ensemble featuring a strapless bodysuit paired with distressed wide-leg denim and a faux-fur shrug, accessorized with heavy metal hardware.\",\"garment_ids\":[2307,2308,2309,2310,2311,2312,2313],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/ecc5f0427c0ee4cdfa51223602046f1d4fee78c0be7e55b990a8eb48aa68ea26.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/ecc5f0427c0ee4cdfa51223602046f1d4fee78c0be7e55b990a8eb48aa68ea26.webp\",\"occasion\":\"night-out\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The look relies on texture contrast between the sleek bodysuit and the fuzzy shrug, balanced by the heavy metal hardware of the belt and chains.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":516,\"public_id\":\"VCQGoQrE4eRr\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-06T15:49:34.184089\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-08T02:19:21.241067\"},{\"name\":\"Sleek Monochrome Minimalist\",\"description\":\"A sharp, monochromatic black ensemble featuring a form-fitting zip-up top and tailored trousers, accented by a classic leather belt.\",\"garment_ids\":[2304,2305,2306],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/926a16392000d623d5b8484339ce75fba344d0006eeaedc42af3f81f49131c19.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/926a16392000d623d5b8484339ce75fba344d0006eeaedc42af3f81f49131c19.webp\",\"occasion\":\"night-out\",\"season\":\"all-season\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The monochromatic black palette creates a sophisticated, streamlined look. The addition of the belt adds necessary definition to the waist.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":515,\"public_id\":\"j3dkdx9mUk85\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-06T15:49:33.563574\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-08T02:19:22.149388\"},{\"name\":\"Y2K-Inspired Graphic Club Look\",\"description\":\"A bold, Y2K-inspired ensemble featuring a graphic animal-print top paired with a black zip-up layer and delicate beaded accessories.\",\"garment_ids\":[2300,2301,2303],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/2eb8b9c2268c62e4c9095aaffeaf101fb8923a7b6965b9f938edb716c47006c4.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/2eb8b9c2268c62e4c9095aaffeaf101fb8923a7b6965b9f938edb716c47006c4.webp\",\"occasion\":\"night-out\",\"season\":\"summer\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"revealing\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The look leans heavily into early 2000s club aesthetics with the combination of animal print, metallic graphics, and beaded accessories.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":514,\"public_id\":\"dP89SHhxCMGr\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-05T18:11:28.997017\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-08T02:19:22.981050\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy All-Black Minimalist\",\"description\":\"A cohesive all-black outfit balancing edgy streetwear elements with minimalist simplicity, featuring a sleeveless tank top, tapered black jeans, chunky lace-up boots, and a structured nylon shoulder bag.\",\"garment_ids\":[2294,2295,2296,2297,2299],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/fbd1027148d981d9ec97c5d5decc986bbe447c0a737f0b8380397b75fa420db1.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/fbd1027148d981d9ec97c5d5decc986bbe447c0a737f0b8380397b75fa420db1.webp\",\"occasion\":\"casual\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This monochromatic all-black outfit demonstrates masterful minimalist styling elevated with intentional edgy details. The chunky lace-up boots and structured nylon bag ground the look in streetwear sensibility, while the sleek black jeans and simple tank keep the overall aesthetic clean and unfussy. The silver jewelry adds a touch of polish without breaking the color harmony. Perfect for an urban casual setting or night out.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":513,\"public_id\":\"H0tIIRJI0sAd\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-29T02:07:49.369417\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-06T07:45:21.881917\"},{\"name\":\"Minimalist Casual Sleeveless Tank & Denim\",\"description\":\"A clean, effortless everyday look featuring a black sleeveless tank paired with mid-rise dark denim jeans. This minimalist ensemble is perfect for casual wear with a timeless, no-fuss aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[2292,2293],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/22e35e5a7eb23e55f7d4a260dfb74473c377575447eb61019b9b3ddd39d53b95.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/22e35e5a7eb23e55f7d4a260dfb74473c377575447eb61019b9b3ddd39d53b95.webp\",\"occasion\":\"casual\",\"season\":\"all-season\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"modest\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This is a quintessential casual basics combination that works year-round. The black tank and dark denim create a cohesive, neutral palette that can be dressed up with accessories or kept simple for everyday wear. This outfit exemplifies the power of quality basics and demonstrates that less can be more in terms of achieving a polished, intentional look.\",\"is_owned\":true,\"is_public\":true,\"id\":512,\"public_id\":\"vXD3w8is2NWR\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-28T18:04:53.452293\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-05T19:09:59.265536\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Rock Chic with Distressed Denim\",\"description\":\"A bold, edgy casual outfit featuring a black cropped hoodie with silver stud embellishments paired with high-waisted distressed dark denim. The look balances feminine silhouette with rock-inspired details and accessories.\",\"garment_ids\":[2289,2290,2291],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/674cbac9dc7da4e39e5c7d1d5bc054d96e3d14784f75ee42d79397f1c9fd6735.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/674cbac9dc7da4e39e5c7d1d5bc054d96e3d14784f75ee42d79397f1c9fd6735.webp\",\"occasion\":\"casual\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit masterfully blends edgy rock elements with casual comfort. The cropped hoodie and high-waisted distressed denim create a flattering silhouette with intentional contrast between fitted and ripped elements. Silver stud detailing adds rebellious polish without feeling costume-y. Best styled with black ankle boots or sleek sneakers to ground the edgy aesthetic.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":511,\"public_id\":\"AxBXkYny3vro\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-28T18:04:08.302232\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-06T07:45:23.165102\"},{\"name\":\"Luxe Blazer & Black Bodysuit Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Luxe, Romantic, Classic, Feminine, Polished. Color palette: Black, Tan, Brown. Key pieces: Blazer, Black Bodysuit, Fur Stole, Handbag. Mood: Elegant, Sophisticated, Feminine, Timeless. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2047,2048,2049,2050],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/7d22afde3ea825fb38d8333d2b09a762d3addb63e9bcd9337a2e724e14cbf054.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/7d22afde3ea825fb38d8333d2b09a762d3addb63e9bcd9337a2e724e14cbf054.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"luxe\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Luxe, Romantic, Classic, Feminine, Polished. Color palette: Black, Tan, Brown. Key pieces: Blazer, Black Bodysuit, Fur Stole, Handbag. Mood: Elegant, Sophisticated, Feminine, Timeless. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":474,\"public_id\":\"zmZcumCurFz7\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.471301\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.471305\"},{\"name\":\"Preppy Blazer & Black Turtleneck Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Preppy, Luxe, Classic, Polished, Vintage-Inspired. Color palette: Black, Burgundy, Cream. Key pieces: Blazer, Black Turtleneck, Belt, Handbag. Mood: Refined, Elegant, Chic, Powerful. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2043,2044,2045,2046],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/9f5bcfe3b4d3906e7056a5c4cba1478b0f79df1ea3ea4310ed7dddba3d4ba0a4.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/9f5bcfe3b4d3906e7056a5c4cba1478b0f79df1ea3ea4310ed7dddba3d4ba0a4.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Preppy, Luxe, Classic, Polished, Vintage-Inspired. Color palette: Black, Burgundy, Cream. Key pieces: Blazer, Black Turtleneck, Belt, Handbag. Mood: Refined, Elegant, Chic, Powerful. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":473,\"public_id\":\"oK6whv90kQIo\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.461079\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.461083\"},{\"name\":\"Minimalist Jacket & Bodysuit Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Minimalist, Edgy, Sleek, Modern, Haute Couture. Color palette: Black, White. Key pieces: Jacket, Bodysuit, Flared Pants, Fur Trim. Mood: Sophisticated, Editorial, Avant-Garde, Confident. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2039,2040,2041,2042],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/6c5162358cee3d4848169a5cf3569c8ebb5c2e4fa8959364a9496d2d002e3d51.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/6c5162358cee3d4848169a5cf3569c8ebb5c2e4fa8959364a9496d2d002e3d51.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Minimalist, Edgy, Sleek, Modern, Haute Couture. Color palette: Black, White. Key pieces: Jacket, Bodysuit, Flared Pants, Fur Trim. Mood: Sophisticated, Editorial, Avant-Garde, Confident. Formality: formal (8/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":472,\"public_id\":\"ALxmv5ccvr0D\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.451277\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.451292\"},{\"name\":\"Business Casual Cardigan & T-Shirt Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Business Casual, Minimalist, Smart Casual, Y2K. Color palette: Black, White, Charcoal. Key pieces: Cardigan, T-Shirt, Cargo Pants, Loafers, Bag. Mood: Polished, Understated, Cool. Formality: casual (5/10). Best for: Spring, Fall.\",\"garment_ids\":[2034,2035,2036,2037,2038],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/a001a58b677ea734dfe4716d30a54f531b83e5e9d06d94ad37c046e5fde1e35c.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/a001a58b677ea734dfe4716d30a54f531b83e5e9d06d94ad37c046e5fde1e35c.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"business casual\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Business Casual, Minimalist, Smart Casual, Y2K. Color palette: Black, White, Charcoal. Key pieces: Cardigan, T-Shirt, Cargo Pants, Loafers, Bag. Mood: Polished, Understated, Cool. Formality: casual (5/10). Best for: Spring, Fall.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":471,\"public_id\":\"8E7iWuGCblsK\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.442603\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-06T07:45:24.643048\"},{\"name\":\"Goth Blazer & Crop Top Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Goth, Edgy, Dark, Glamorous. Color palette: Black, Ivory, Gold. Key pieces: Blazer, Crop Top, Midi Skirt, Heels, Fur Stole. Mood: Edgy, Sophisticated, Moody. Formality: smart casual (7/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2029,2030,2031,2032,2033],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/9f64bf112ddc33242c9a45370caff0942276d7f7be38ad6c7783e53741b8857a.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/9f64bf112ddc33242c9a45370caff0942276d7f7be38ad6c7783e53741b8857a.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"goth\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Goth, Edgy, Dark, Glamorous. Color palette: Black, Ivory, Gold. Key pieces: Blazer, Crop Top, Midi Skirt, Heels, Fur Stole. Mood: Edgy, Sophisticated, Moody. Formality: smart casual (7/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":470,\"public_id\":\"i9zCDVlbyCi8\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.433324\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.433328\"},{\"name\":\"Casual Hoodie & Denim Skirt Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Casual, Streetwear, Rural, Y2K. Color palette: Tan, Brown, Denim Blue. Key pieces: Hoodie, Denim Skirt, Boots. Mood: Casual, Carefree, Playful. Formality: very casual (3/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2026,2027,2028],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/7ffdb64a719818b5d8bb1d4ed4698e55c304da9c9c9c72d3ddb325a98ab64c97.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/7ffdb64a719818b5d8bb1d4ed4698e55c304da9c9c9c72d3ddb325a98ab64c97.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"casual\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Casual, Streetwear, Rural, Y2K. Color palette: Tan, Brown, Denim Blue. Key pieces: Hoodie, Denim Skirt, Boots. Mood: Casual, Carefree, Playful. Formality: very casual (3/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":469,\"public_id\":\"GMYkRMoH4CTR\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.423221\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.423225\"},{\"name\":\"Goth Blazer & Crop Top Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Goth, Edgy, Dark Academia, Y2K. Color palette: Black, Gray, Silver. Key pieces: Blazer, Crop Top, Mini Skirt, Loafers, Bag. Mood: Edgy, Polished, Moody. Formality: smart casual (6/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2021,2022,2023,2024,2025],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/509fc5efa53e016c96002955f067225963ad0bba95423cafcf0f184ad55d6b00.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/509fc5efa53e016c96002955f067225963ad0bba95423cafcf0f184ad55d6b00.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"goth\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Goth, Edgy, Dark Academia, Y2K. Color palette: Black, Gray, Silver. Key pieces: Blazer, Crop Top, Mini Skirt, Loafers, Bag. Mood: Edgy, Polished, Moody. Formality: smart casual (6/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":468,\"public_id\":\"CF8419Ezkh1k\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.415715\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.415719\"},{\"name\":\"Minimalist Off-Shoulder Sweater & Jeans Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Minimalist, Smart Casual, Cozy, Contemporary. Color palette: Cream, Denim Blue, Beige. Key pieces: Off-Shoulder Sweater, Jeans, Knee-High Boots, Shoulder Bag. Mood: Cozy, Polished, Effortless. Formality: smart casual (6/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"garment_ids\":[2017,2018,2019,2020],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/054dab03a4b624a083e9801bfc8da2a96e1ce6c746412a2e3aeb1d538ebbcb5a.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/054dab03a4b624a083e9801bfc8da2a96e1ce6c746412a2e3aeb1d538ebbcb5a.webp\",\"occasion\":null,\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":null,\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":null,\"ai_notes\":\"Style: Minimalist, Smart Casual, Cozy, Contemporary. Color palette: Cream, Denim Blue, Beige. Key pieces: Off-Shoulder Sweater, Jeans, Knee-High Boots, Shoulder Bag. Mood: Cozy, Polished, Effortless. Formality: smart casual (6/10). Best for: Fall, Winter.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":467,\"public_id\":\"mrBOz6RFizjH\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.405592\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T21:09:04.405596\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Leather Jacket & Crop Top Look\",\"description\":\"Style: Edgy, Streetwear, Preppy, Casual. Color palette: Black, Cream, Burgundy. Key pieces: Leather Jacket, Crop Top, Pleated Mini Skirt, Knee-High Boots, Fishnet Tights. Mood: Edgy, Youthful, Confident. Formality: casual (5/10). Best for: Spring, Fall.\",\"garment_ids\":[2012,2013,2014,2015,2016],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c99214e76180cddbd8d9cb0b23ded878205fc721b330365