omatic black outfit featuring a long wool coat over a mini dress, creating an elegant and streamlined silhouette perfect for cooler weather.\",\"garment_ids\":[65,66,67,68,69],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/59baab56f3c6b8465729a40ab3ff1659c31d43d746ef2a3c7eaa0f2304184669.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/59baab56f3c6b8465729a40ab3ff1659c31d43d746ef2a3c7eaa0f2304184669.webp\",\"occasion\":\"City strolling, casual business meetings, dinner dates\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"minimalist\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The monochromatic black palette creates a sleek, sophisticated look. The long coat adds drama while the mini dress provides a subtle feminine touch. Perfect example of elevated minimalism.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":13,\"public_id\":\"Go7WcqIqPQV5\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:51:07.192347\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:58.197952\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy Black Monochrome with Leather Jacket\",\"description\":\"A sleek all-black ensemble featuring a cropped leather moto jacket over a fitted black dress, creating a modern edgy aesthetic with gothic undertones.\",\"garment_ids\":[60,61,64,63],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/2fed86f523d572f6635f73e22da4fe3918b9c72571a5830715c158d934c8ef1c.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/2fed86f523d572f6635f73e22da4fe3918b9c72571a5830715c158d934c8ef1c.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, concerts, or date nights\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The all-black palette with leather textures creates a strong, confident look. The layered necklaces add subtle detail without disrupting the monochrome theme.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":12,\"public_id\":\"QWTVehbV0FBi\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:50:40.710075\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:57.798247\"},{\"name\":\"Preppy Academia Brown Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A cohesive brown-toned outfit featuring layered textures and preppy elements with a turtleneck, corduroy jacket, plaid mini skirt, and knee-high boots. The monochromatic brown palette creates a sophisticated autumn look with academic styling.\",\"garment_ids\":[54,55,56,58,59],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/92421b0fb8478a770650f054aa7c002a581394a86b8001cd81158c38ee9ba61d.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/92421b0fb8478a770650f054aa7c002a581394a86b8001cd81158c38ee9ba61d.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, coffee dates, university campus\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The monochromatic brown palette with varying textures creates visual interest while maintaining sophistication. The white socks add a playful touch to the otherwise polished look.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":11,\"public_id\":\"KXh230OgKaKy\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:50:12.408772\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:46.493479\"},{\"name\":\"Cozy Off-Shoulder Sweater Look\",\"description\":\"A relaxed yet stylish outfit featuring an oversized gray off-shoulder sweater paired with a black mini skirt, polka dot tights, and cozy fur-trimmed boots for a perfect casual-chic winter ensemble.\",\"garment_ids\":[49,50,51,52,53],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/430a254b949711a94b4e5a55f2be53d82310757a4212dfa2b0bf77365c88b74b.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/430a254b949711a94b4e5a55f2be53d82310757a4212dfa2b0bf77365c88b74b.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee dates, shopping\",\"season\":\"fall/winter\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"romantic\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The off-shoulder sweater creates an effortlessly feminine look while the polka dot tights add a playful touch. The contrast between the oversized top and fitted bottom creates a flattering silhouette.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":10,\"public_id\":\"j1tXdBNWl4xS\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:49:41.042106\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:45.757147\"},{\"name\":\"Edgy All-Black Winter Look\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated all-black ensemble featuring textural contrasts between knits and leather, with chain details adding an edgy urban aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[43,44,45,48,47],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/1b5b4cb5a06770b1d706efe19c2961ccb7324d11c71920c619e2465e7ef9afd7.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/1b5b4cb5a06770b1d706efe19c2961ccb7324d11c71920c619e2465e7ef9afd7.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, coffee dates, urban exploration\",\"season\":\"fall/winter\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The all-black palette creates sophistication while chain details add edge; consider adding silver jewelry to complement the boot hardware\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":9,\"public_id\":\"SL9Hhwj3D0ua\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:49:14.126424\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:45.381334\"},{\"name\":\"Academic Gothic Layered Look\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated layered ensemble featuring a gray cable-knit sweater with decorative buckled vest over a pleated mini skirt, creating a dark academia aesthetic with gothic undertones.\",\"garment_ids\":[39,40,41,42],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/7473bda803d9af3f7803b7b2709255d3dd87a6623fa524832b88853e1db00476.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/7473bda803d9af3f7803b7b2709255d3dd87a6623fa524832b88853e1db00476.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outing, coffee date, or creative workplace\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"vintage\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The layered approach with the buckled vest creates visual interest while maintaining a sophisticated academic aesthetic. The over-the-knee socks add a playful contrast to the structured pieces.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":8,\"public_id\":\"ReSUcTkc0ZA8\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:48:43.316255\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:44.867149\"},{\"name\":\"Monochromatic Gothic Ensemble\",\"description\":\"An all-black coordinated look featuring a ribbed cardigan and mini skirt set with platform boots, accessorized with gold jewelry and retro sunglasses for an edgy yet feminine aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[29,30,31,32,37,35],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/0064e9c9e99b48562f54bbc06c88adc5867a14762ec1bfe2673c61823e60a3a1.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/0064e9c9e99b48562f54bbc06c88adc5867a14762ec1bfe2673c61823e60a3a1.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, concerts, or creative events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The coordinated knit set creates a polished foundation while platform boots and retro accessories add personality and edge\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":7,\"public_id\":\"6GOxNv1yQsl7\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:48:16.371493\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:43.717712\"},{\"name\":\"Vintage Bow Blouse with Pleated Maxi\",\"description\":\"An elegant vintage-inspired ensemble featuring a sage green pussy bow blouse paired with a dramatic black pleated maxi skirt and tall boots.\",\"garment_ids\":[26,27,28],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/03abe36025b6fa2ff01ea2a013b3a0050db57cc39030b1c5e021c12c0d1676e1.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/03abe36025b6fa2ff01ea2a013b3a0050db57cc39030b1c5e021c12c0d1676e1.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Date night, cultural events, or sophisticated daywear\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"vintage\",\"coverage\":\"conservative\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The contrast between the earthy green top and dramatic black skirt creates visual interest, while the pussy bow adds vintage charm and the pleated skirt provides movement and elegance\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":6,\"public_id\":\"mkwcaDn81g1V\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:47:46.132566\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:42.643213\"},{\"name\":\"Bohemian Duster with Dark Romance\",\"description\":\"A dramatic bohemian look featuring a flowing neutral duster coat layered over dark pieces, creating an edgy romantic aesthetic perfect for golden hour photography.\",\"garment_ids\":[19,20,21,22,23,24,25],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/430dce0919cb73b80a3e27c0d34eb2bf4159442744d7fbb6e8e9fe03147e5378.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/430dce0919cb73b80a3e27c0d34eb2bf4159442744d7fbb6e8e9fe03147e5378.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual day out, photography session, or festival\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"bohemian\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The flowing duster creates beautiful movement while the fitted base layers and structured boots ground the look. The contrast between light and dark pieces adds visual interest and depth.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":5,\"public_id\":\"tD4wSlDG54RC\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T07:47:21.595130\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:42.319215\"},{\"name\":\"Winter Wonderland Kawaii Style\",\"description\":\"A playful winter outfit featuring a white fur-trimmed hoodie with graphic details, paired with thigh-high boots and decorative leg accessories for an anime-inspired aesthetic.\",\"garment_ids\":[14,15,16,17,18],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/f8f62209f28d18b5df45255c4d7e42fb83a9eed2165f7b04e336bb86a0408236.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/f8f62209f28d18b5df45255c4d7e42fb83a9eed2165f7b04e336bb86a0408236.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, anime conventions, creative events\",\"season\":\"winter\",\"formality\":\"casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"streetwear\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit combines kawaii/anime-inspired elements with practical winter wear, featuring dramatic proportions and playful layering\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":4,\"public_id\":\"cseDfBZCnKKl\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T06:57:09.997223\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:42.207408\"},{\"name\":\"Gothic Lolita Corset Ensemble\",\"description\":\"A dramatic all-black gothic outfit featuring a corset dress with ruffled layers and thigh-high lace-up boots, creating a bold alternative fashion statement.\",\"garment_ids\":[9,10,11,12,13],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/4c500548abec20eb7b0bc634d9fb35b91296c83e3e53b079be57d5c3ef46e1cd.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/4c500548abec20eb7b0bc634d9fb35b91296c83e3e53b079be57d5c3ef46e1cd.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Alternative fashion events, gothic clubs, costume parties\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"semi-formal\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"This outfit showcases gothic lolita fashion with dramatic silhouettes, bondage-inspired accessories, and intricate lacing details throughout\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":3,\"public_id\":\"ifUJr03y37iO\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T06:53:16.715817\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:41.215581\"},{\"name\":\"All-Black Edgy Chic Look\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated all-black ensemble featuring a ribbed turtleneck sweater paired with a leather mini skirt, creating a sleek and edgy aesthetic perfect for urban styling.\",\"garment_ids\":[4,5,6,7,8],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/c36659de861693c47084b8de15a696219927d1bf746985140a88d1695d8aaf51.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/c36659de861693c47084b8de15a696219927d1bf746985140a88d1695d8aaf51.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Date night, urban outings, or evening events\",\"season\":\"fall\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"edgy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"Monochromatic black creates a sleek silhouette while leather elements add edge and texture contrast to the soft knit top\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":2,\"public_id\":\"8c89rWFtAVUA\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T06:52:52.867095\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:38.212531\"},{\"name\":\"Preppy School-Inspired Look\",\"description\":\"A modern take on school uniform styling featuring a cropped white corset top with dramatic ruffled sleeves paired with a charcoal pleated mini skirt.\",\"garment_ids\":[3,2],\"image_url\":\"/uploads/shared/54851eac81cf576fec19e9ec0ed988c2f99295ae18da3f09e5d78ba6d4d04f76.webp\",\"image_path\":\"shared/54851eac81cf576fec19e9ec0ed988c2f99295ae18da3f09e5d78ba6d4d04f76.webp\",\"occasion\":\"Casual outings, social events, or creative work environments\",\"season\":\"spring\",\"formality\":\"smart-casual\",\"style_vibe\":\"preppy\",\"coverage\":\"moderate\",\"user_rating\":null,\"style_score\":75.0,\"ai_notes\":\"The combination of structured corsetry with soft ruffled sleeves creates an interesting contrast between romantic and preppy aesthetics. The layering technique adds depth and sophistication to the look.\",\"is_owned\":false,\"is_public\":false,\"id\":1,\"public_id\":\"GcV74hzAcYJb\",\"user_id\":1,\"worn_count\":0,\"last_worn\":null,\"image_variants\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-26T06:52:29.007101\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-26T19:36:32.879110\"}]"
